WEBVTT

00:03:57.182 --> 00:04:00.660
Or maybe you'd like to build
a stronger connection,

00:04:00.684 --> 00:04:05.134
but you have a lot
of questions and concerns.

00:04:05.158 --> 00:04:08.357
You're what I might call "bridge curious."

00:04:08.381 --> 00:04:12.665
(Laughter)

00:04:12.689 --> 00:04:14.123
Here are some possible reasons

00:04:14.147 --> 00:04:16.736
why some of you
may avoid depressed people.

00:04:17.807 --> 00:04:19.006
You might be afraid

00:04:19.030 --> 00:04:21.724
that if you talk to somebody
while they're depressed,

00:04:21.748 --> 00:04:24.410
you're suddenly responsible
for their well-being.

00:04:25.521 --> 00:04:28.519
You're not expected to be Dr. Phil.

00:04:28.965 --> 00:04:30.156
Just be friendly --